com.gams.api

Class GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gams.api.GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation

  • public class GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation stores a domain violation information for each symbol in a GAMSDatabase instance. It contains information of which GAMSSymbol instance whose domain is violated and a list of GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation instances containing all domain violation records of the GAMSSymbol instance.
    See Also:
    GAMSDatabase.checkDomains(), GAMSDatabase.getDatabaseDomainViolations(int, int), GAMSSymbolDomainViolation, GAMSSymbol.checkDomains(), GAMSSymbol.getSymbolDomainViolations(int)
